        "body": "## Summary\n\n- add the plugin-state runtime SDK subpath plus a sync keyed-store API backed by the existing sidecar SQLite DB\n- migrate Discord model picker preferences and Feishu dedupe state onto plugin state, with doctor import plans for existing JSON state\n- align Feishu host/plugin API metadata, shrinkwrap, official channel catalog, and docs with the new plugin-state runtime requirement\n- fix an upstream doctor e2e lint issue that blocked the post-rebase changed gate\n\n## Verification\n\n- `pnpm plugin-sdk:api:check`\n- `git diff --check`\n- `pnpm format:docs:check`\n- `pnpm test src/plugin-state/plugin-state-store.test.ts src/plugin-state/plugin-state-store.runtime.test.ts src/plugins/contracts/plugin-sdk-package-contract-guardrails.test.ts src/channels/plugins/bundled.shape-guard.test.ts src/commands/doctor-state-migrations.test.ts extensions/discord/setup-entry.test.ts extensions/discord/src/monitor/model-picker-preferences-migrations.test.ts extensions/discord/src/monitor/model-picker-preferences.test.ts extensions/feishu/setup-entry.test.ts extensions/feishu/src/dedup-migrations.test.ts extensions/feishu/src/dedup.test.ts`\n- `pnpm test src/commands/doctor.runs-legacy-state-migrations-yes-mode-without.e2e.test.ts`\n- `env -u OPENCLAW_TESTBOX pnpm check:changed`\n- autoreview clean: no accepted/actionable findings\n\n## Real behavior proof\n\nBehavior addressed: existing Discord model-picker JSON and Feishu dedupe JSON files are detected by doctor and imported into plugin-state sidecar SQLite entries, then archived by the migration framework.\nReal environment tested: local source checkout on macOS with Node/pnpm repo wrappers.\nExact steps or command run after this patch: focused plugin-state, doctor, Discord, Feishu, package contract, docs formatting, API baseline, and changed-file gates listed above.\nEvidence after fix: migration tests cover Discord JSON import, Feishu TTL-preserving dedupe import, expired-only Feishu skip behavior,